dict.acceptation: 力量；优点，长处；（光、声、色等的）力度；人力[数]；

sent.orig: The next three, INTELLIGENCE, STRENGTH, and SPEED, are the actual attributes being set.
sent.trans: 接下来的三条INTELLIGENCE、STRENGTH、SPEED是实际被设置的属性。

sent.orig: Strength and power indicate an internal quality of an object or person.
sent.trans: strength和power表示物体或人的内在特性。

sent.orig: ECC is one of the known public crypto Methods: That provide the best strength-per-bit.
sent.trans: 椭圆曲线密码体制(Elliptic Curve Cryptosystem,ECC)是目前已知的所有公钥密码体制中能提供最高比特强度(strength-per-bit)的一种公钥加密体制。

sent.orig: Bending strength, compressive strength, interfacial bond strength and frost resistance are also studied and analyzed.
sent.trans: 并对修补混凝土的抗折、抗压、新老界面粘结强度以及抗冻性等进行了试验研究。

sent.orig: The tensile strength, impact strength, flexural strength, thermal properties and morphology of the composites were investigated.
sent.trans: 研究了复合材料的拉伸强度、冲击强度、弯曲强度、形态及热性能。
